\c 3
\s Masvingo namasuwo eJerusarema anovakwazve
\p
\v 1 Ipapo Eriashibhi mupristi mukuru akasimuka, nehama dzake vapristi, vakavaka suwo ramakwai; vakariita dzvene, nokutimika magonhi aro; vakariita dzvene kusvikira pashongwe yeHamea nokushongwe yeHananeri.
\v 2 Kurutivi rwake kwakavakwa navarume veJeriko. Kurutivi rwavo kwakavakwa naZakuri mwanakomana waImiri.
\v 3 Suwo rehove rakavakwa navanakomana vaHasenaa; ivo vakaisa matanda aro, nokutimika magonhi aro, nekiyi dzaro, namazariro aro.
\v 4 Kurutivi rwavo kwakagadzirwa naMeremoti mwanakomana waUriya, mwanakomana waHakozi. Kurutivi rwavo rwakagadzirwa naMeshurami mwanakomana waBherekia, mwanakomana waMeshezabheri. Kurutivi rwavo kwakagadzirwa naZadhoki mwanakomana waBhaana.
\v 5 Kurutivi rwavo kwakagadzirwa navaTekoi; asi vakuru pakati pavo havana kuisa mitsipa yavo pabasa rashe wavo.
\v 6 Suwo rekare rakagadzirwa naJoyadha mwanakomana waPasea, naMeshurami mwanakomana waBhesodheya; ivo vakaisa matanda aro, nokutimika magonhi aro, nekiyi dzaro, namazariro aro.
\v 7 Kurutivi rwavo kwakagadzirwa naMeratia muGibhiyoni, naJadhoni muMeronoti, navarume veGibhiyoni neMizipa, vaiva voushe hwomubati mhiri korwizi.
\v 8 Kurutivi rwake kwakagadzirwa naUzieri mwanakomana waHarihaya, vapfuri vegoridhe. Kurutivi rwake kwakagadzirwa naHanania, umwe wavavhenganisi vezvinonhuhwira; ivo vakasimbisa Jerusarema kusvikira parusvingo rwakafara.
\v 9 Kurutivi rwavo kwakagadzirwa naRefaya mwanakomana waHuri, mubati wehafu yenyika yeJerusarema.
\v 10 Kurutivi rwavo kwakagadzirwa naJedhaya mwanakomana waHarumafi, pakatarisana neimba yake. Kurutivi rwake kwakagadzirwa naHatushi mwanakomana waHashabheneya.
\v 11 Marikia mwanakomana waHarimi, naHashubhi mwanakomana waPahatimoabhi, vakagadzira rumwe rutivi, neshongwe yamavira.
\v 12 Kurutivi rwake kwakagadzirwa naSharumi mwanakomana waHaroheshi, mubati wehafu yenyika yeJerusarema, iye navakunda vake.
\v 13 Suwo romupata rakagadzirwa naHanuni navakange vagere Zanowa; ivo vakarivaka, vakatimika magonhi aro, nekiyi dzaro, namazariro aro, namakubhiti ane chiuru chimwe orusvingo kusvikira pasuwo ramarara.
\v 14 Suwo ramarara rakagadzirwa naMarikiya mwanakomana waRekabhi, mubati wenyika yeBhetihakeremi; iye akarivaka, nokutimika magonhi aro, nekiyi dzaro, namazariro aro.
\v 15 Suwo retsime rakagadzirwa naSharumi mwanakomana waKorihoze, mubati wenyika yeMizipa; iye akarivaka, akariisa denga, akatimika magonhi aro, nekiyi dzaro, namazariro aro, uye rusvingo rwedziva reShera pamunda wamambo, kusvikira pamatanho anoburuka achibva muguta raDhavhidhi.
\v 16 Akamutevera pakugadzira akange ari Nehemiya mwanakomana waAzibhuki, mubati wehafu yenyika yeBhetizuri, kusvikira pakatarisana namarinda aDhavhidhi, uye kusvikira padziva rakange ravakwa, nokuimba yemagamba.
\v 17 Vakamutevera pakugadzira vakange vari VaRevhi: Rehumi mwanakomana waBhani, nokurutivi rwake kwakagadzirwa naHashabhia mubati wehafu yenyika yeKeira, panzvimbo yenyika yake.
\v 18 Hama dzavo ndidzo dzakamutevera pakugadzira, Bhavhai mwanakomana waHenadhadhi, mubati wehafu yenyika yeKeira.
\v 19 Kurutivi rwake Ezeri mwanakomana waJeshua, mubati weMizipa, akagadzira umwe mupanda, pakatarisana neimba yenhumbi dzehondo, pakona yorusvingo.
\v 20 Bharuki mwanakomana waZabhai wakamutevera akagadzira nokushingaira umwe mupanda, kubva pakona yorusvingo kusvikira pamukova weimba yaEriashibhi mupristi mukuru.
\v 21 Meremoti mwanakomana waUriya, mwanakomana waHakozi, akamutevera akagadzira umwe mupanda, kubva pamukova weimba yaEriashibhi, kusvikira pakuguma kweimba yaEriashibhi.
\v 22 Vapristi, varume vebani, vakamutevera iye pakugadzira pakapoteredza imba yake.
\v 23 Bhenjamini naHashubhi ndivo vakavatevera pakugadzira pakatarisana neimba yavo. Azaria mwanakomana waMaaseya, mwanakomana waAnania, akavatevera pakugadzira parutivi rweimba yake.
\v 24 Bhinui mwanakomana waHenadhadhi akamutevera pakugadzira umwe mupanda, kubva paimba yaAzaria kusvikira pakona yorusvingo, kundosvikazve pakona.
\v 25 Parari mwanakomana waUzai akagadzira pakatarisana nekona yorusvingo, neshongwe inobuda paimba yokumusoro yamambo, iri paruvazhe rwavarindi. Pedhaya mwanakomana waParoshi akamutevera.
\v 26 Zvino vaNetinimi vaigara Oferi, kusvikira pakatarisana nesuwo remvura kurutivi rwamabvazuva rweshongwe yakabuda kunze.
\v 27 VaTekoi vakamutevera pakugadzira umwe mupanda pakatarisana neshongwe huru yakabuda kunze, kundosvikira parusvingo rweOferi.
\v 28 Vapristi vakagadzira pamusoro pesuwo ramabhiza, umwe neumwe pakatarisana neimba yake.
\v 29 Zadhoki mwanakomana waImeri akavatevera pakugadzira pakatarisana neimba yake. Shemaya mwanakomana waShekania, murindi wesuwo rokumabvazuva, akamutevera pakugadzira.
\v 30 Hanania mwanakomana waSheremia naHanuni mwanakomana wechitanhatu waZarafi ndiye vakamutevera pakugadzira umwe mupanda. Meshurami mwanakomana waBherekia, akamutevera pakugadzira pakatarisana neimba yake.
\v 31 Marikiya umwe wavapfuri vegoridhe, wakamutevera pakugadzira kusvikira kudzimba dzavaNetinimi nedzavatengesi, pakatarisana nesuwo raHamifekadhi, kusvikira pakamuri yokumusoro iri paimba.
\v 32 Pakati peimba yokumusoro pakona nesuwo ramakwai, pakagadzirwa navapfuri vegoridhe navatengesi.
